On 5/14/07, Kent Frazier  wrote:
snip
> Can someone with a more honed eye for this code tell me what I am doing wrong?
snip

You are never printing anything.  Try

#!perl -w
use strict;

$^I = ".bak";
while (<>) {
    if ( /^#!/ ) {
        $_ .= "## Copyright (C) 2007 by Kent Frazier.\n";
    }
    print;
}

